     <div type="translators_note">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <p>¶ This was brought vnto me in Englysshe of an olde translacyon / rughe / and rude / and requyred to amende it. I thought lesse labour to wryte newe the whole / and I haue done vnto the sentēce not very nere the letter / and in dyuers places added some thynges folo<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>wyng vpon the same to make the mater more sentencyoue / and full. I beseche you take all vnto the best / and pray for the olde wretched brother of Syon Rycharde whytforde.</p>
